OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FPlans to start using chemicals to
OL,7,Ftackle weeds on pavements in Cornwall
OL,8,Fhave been put on hold following major
OL,9,Fbacklash from residents.
OL,11,FMore than 7,500 people have signed a
OL,12,Fpetition against Cornwall Council's
OL,13,Fplans to reintroduce a controversial
OL,14,Fweedkiller.
OL,16,FThe council stopped using chemicals to
OL,17,Fremove weeds from highways 13 years
OL,18,Fago but then announced the targeted
OL,19,Fapplication of glyphosate was planned
OL,20,Fto re-start next month.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
