OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FThe issue was hotly debated at a full
OL,7,Fmeeting of the council on Tuesday 21
OL,8,FApril. Dozens of protestors gathered
OL,9,Foutside New County Hall in Truro ahead
OL,10,Fof the meeting which received huge
OL,11,Fnumbers of questions from the public.
OL,13,FAmong those waiting to greet
OL,14,Fcouncillors arriving to discuss the
OL,15,Fweedkiller issue were beekeepers and
OL,16,Fmedical professionals.
OL,18,FThe council defended its plan, saying
OL,19,Fthe chemical would only be used on
OL,20,Fsafety grounds, in situations where
OL,21,Fweeds were causing access issues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FThey also said there would not be a
OL,7,F"blanket spraying" plan and that local
OL,8,Ftown and parish councils could opt out.
OL,10,FRick Bowers, a retired doctor, was one
OL,11,Fof those protesting outside the
OL,12,Fmeeting. He said: "I came along
OL,13,Fbecause I wanted to say to Cornwall
OL,14,FCouncil, as a medical practitioner,
OL,15,Fthat for the sake of our health and
OL,16,Four environment they must please not
OL,17,Fstart using glyphosate weedkiller.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"As someone who is a scientist and
OL,7,Fconcerned about the environment I want
OL,8,Fto say that we depend on our
OL,9,Fenvironment for the air we breathe,
OL,10,Fthe water we drink and the soil that
OL,11,Fgrows the food we eat and we must not
OL,12,Fbe poisoning our environment with
OL,13,Fweedkillers.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"I was very angry, particularly as a
OL,7,Fparish councillor, we were given three
OL,8,Fweeks to opt out of the weed-killing
OL,9,Fand and considerable penalties in
OL,10,Fterms of funding if we didn't opt out
OL,11,Fin terms of weed removal, so that
OL,12,Fmotivated me to come, out of anger of
OL,13,Fhaving this imposed on us with no
OL,14,Fprior discussion."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FLemi Mitchell and her son Luke also
OL,7,Fjoined the protest. Ms Mitchell said:
OL,8,F"I feel we are going backwards rather
OL,9,Fthan forwards, so the use of this
OL,10,Fchemical will cause that to go further
OL,11,Fand at the end of the day it's his
OL,12,Ffuture and it is going to affect his
OL,13,Ffuture as well as everything else so
OL,14,Fit's just poison they're spraying and
OL,15,Fit's not good."
OL,17,FLuke added: "I feel like the bees
OL,18,Fshouldn't die, they're trying to kill
OL,19,Fweeds but they are going to kill bees,
OL,20,Fmoths and all of that."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@OO]yD@MOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FCampaigners claimed that more people
OL,7,Fsigned their petition against the use
OL,8,Fof the weedkiller than have complained
OL,9,Fto Cornwall Council in recent years
OL,10,Fabout weeds.
OL,12,FOne of the protestors at the meeting
OL,13,Fwas beekeeper Nichola Andersen from
OL,14,FTruro. She said: "We have come along
OL,15,Fbecause we are very concerned about
OL,16,Fglyphosate being sprayed in our
OL,17,Fstreets and where there are people
OL,18,Faround and wildlife and getting rid of
OL,19,Fthe so-called weeds, which are really
OL,20,Fwildflowers.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"We understand about one invasive
OL,7,Fweed, Japanese Knotweed, and we
OL,8,Funderstand that it has to be gotten
OL,9,Frid of, but everything else would be a
OL,10,Fretrograde step.
OL,12,F"Myself and my friends who are also
OL,13,Fbee keepers have lost bees due to
OL,14,Fspraying in fields with glyphosate and
OL,15,Fother chemicals and it's horrible
OL,16,Fwatching them die being poisoned like
OL,17,Fthat. We're hoping by coming here we
OL,18,Fare showing the councillors they don't
OL,19,Fhave public support for this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"Just go back to doing it the old
OL,7,Ffashioned way, dig them out, it's not
OL,8,Fhard we all do it in our gardens, they
OL,9,Fare just using the spray as a lazy way
OL,10,Fof dealing with this. It's not very
OL,11,Ftargeted and that means they just kill
OL,12,Feverything.
OL,14,FAhead of the meeting, Cornwall Council
OL,15,Fsaid it had an unprecedented number of
OL,16,Fquestions from the public, including
OL,17,F40 relating to the use of weedkiller.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FCouncillor Dan Rogerson, portfolio
OL,7,Fholder for transport, responded to the
OL,8,Fquestions which he said raised
OL,9,Fconcerns about public health,
OL,10,Fbiodiversity, bees and water quality.
OL,12,FHe told the meeting: "This is not
OL,13,Fsimply about appearance, it is also
OL,14,Fabout accessibility, safety and
OL,15,Fprotecting the highway access.
OL,26,@tD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"This decision is not a return to
OL,7,Fblanket spraying. It forms part of a
OL,8,Ftime limited three-year recovery
OL,9,Fprogramme alongside increased
OL,10,Finvestment in biodiversity
OL,11,Fconservation and community
OL,12,Fvolunteering.
OL,14,F"Glyphosate will only be used where
OL,15,Fweeds are present, only on hard urban
OL,16,Fhighway surfaces and applied using
OL,17,Fmodern control drop application to
OL,18,Fgreatly reduce any drift.
OL,20,F"Public open spaces and other grassed
OL,21,Fareas will not be treated.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,F"National regulations currently allow
OL,7,Fglyphosate to be used in the UK and
OL,8,Fevidence shows using in a careful way,
OL,9,Fonly on hard surfaces, public exposure
OL,10,Fand therefore health risks are low.
OL,12,F"Town and parish councils may opt out
OL,13,Fif they wish to manage areas without
OL,14,Fchemicals providing standards are
OL,15,Fmaintained."
OL,17,FThe meeting overwhelmingly passed a
OL,18,Fmotion which agreed to pause the use
OL,19,Fof chemical weed treatment until a
OL,20,Fmeaningful public consultation process
OL,21,Fhas been completed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776888354
OL,3,CControversial plans to reintroduce
OL,4,Cchemical weedkiller in Cornwall paused
OL,6,FThe motion also recognised the wholly
OL,7,Finadequate three week opt out window
OL,8,Fprovided to parish and town councils
OL,9,Fwhich included Easter and commits to
OL,10,Fextending this to 30 days after the
OL,11,Fpublic consultation results have been
OL,12,Fpublished and also review the
OL,13,Ffinancial terms of any scheme for them
OL,14,Fto opt out.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
